description: Manage backends of Front Door backend pools.

commands.name: az network front-door backend-pool backend add
commands.summary: Add a backend to a Front Door backend pool.
commands.syntax:
az network front-door backend-pool backend add --address
                                               --front-door-name
                                               --pool-name
                                               --resource-group
                                               [--approval-message]
                                               [--backend-host-header]
                                               [--disabled {false, true}]
                                               [--http-port]
                                               [--https-port]
                                               [--priority]
                                               [--private-link-alias]
                                               [--private-link-location]
                                               [--private-link-resource-id]
                                               [--weight]

commands.name: az network front-door backend-pool backend list
commands.summary: List backends of a Front Door backend pool.
commands.syntax:
az network front-door backend-pool backend list --front-door-name
                                                --pool-name
                                                --resource-group

commands.name: az network front-door backend-pool backend remove
commands.summary: Remove a backend from a Front Door backend pool.
commands.syntax:
az network front-door backend-pool backend remove --front-door-name
                                                  --index
                                                  --pool-name
                                                  --resource-group

commands.name: az network front-door backend-pool backend update
commands.summary: Update a backend to a Front Door backend pool.
commands.syntax:
az network front-door backend-pool backend update --front-door-name
                                                  --index
                                                  --pool-name
                                                  --resource-group
                                                  [--address]
                                                  [--approval-message]
                                                  [--backend-host-header]
                                                  [--disabled {false, true}]
                                                  [--http-port]
                                                  [--https-port]
                                                  [--priority]
                                                  [--private-link-alias]
                                                  [--private-link-location]
                                                  [--private-link-resource-id]
                                                  [--weight]
